{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6b9b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4271"},"text":"§ 4271.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Program cost, fielding, and performance goals in planning major defense acquisition programs","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6b9c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Program Cost and Fielding Targets","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6b9d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Before funds are obligated for technology development, systems development, or production of a major defense acquisition program, the designated milestone decision authority for the program shall ensure, by establishing the goals described in paragraph (2), that the program will—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6b9e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" be affordable;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6b9f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" incorporate program planning that anticipates the evolution of capabilities to meet changing threats, technology insertion, and interoperability; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" be fielded when needed.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The goals described in this paragraph are goals for—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the procurement unit cost and sustainment cost (referred to in this section as the “program cost targets”);","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the date for initial operational capability (referred to in this section as the “fielding target”); and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/a/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" technology maturation, prototyping, and a modular open system approach to evolve system capabilities and improve interoperability.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Definitions","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “procurement unit cost” has the meaning provided in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4351/a/2"},"text":"section 4351(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s4271/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “initial capabilities document” has the meaning provided in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4251/d/1"},"text":"section 4251(d)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa6e6ba8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/328/dA/tVIII/s807/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–328, div. A, title VIII, § 807(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/2260"},"text":"130 Stat. 2260","children":[],"tail":", § 2448a; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s831/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 8